author_ssm: John M. Sapp, Brent Phillips, Cristina Vignone
unittitle_ssm: Queer|Art|Film Collection
abstract_ssm: Queer|Art|Film is a monthly film series hosted by the Independent Film Channel (IFC) Center where queer artists exhibit and speak about their favorite films.  The Queer|Art|Film Collection contains video documentation, posters, and flyers.
